products.title: Kellogg's Moons & Stars Cereals Chocos
products.description: Nourishing & Solid Breakfast/Snack: Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars is a nourishing & solid breakfast/evening snack option for kids. It makes milk chocolaty & crunchy and fills your kid’s tummy, giving them the Energy to stay active & fun! Packed with Nutrients: Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars is made with Whole Grain & is a source of Fiber that fills your kid’s tummy. It is high in Calcium & Protein that fuel your child’s growing body. It has 10 essential vitamins & minerals like Iron, Zinc, B Vitamins & Vitamin C for your active kids. Gives your kid 66% Calcium & 31% Protein of a Day’s Requirement: 30g Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars + 200ml cow’s milk provides 66% of the day’s RDA for Calcium and 31% of the day’s RDA for Protein. Makes Milk Chocolaty & Crunchy: Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars makes milk chocolaty and crunchy so your kid will love it!
products.key_features:
Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars is a nourishing & solid breakfast for kids. It makes milk chocolaty and delicious.
Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars has the goodness of Whole Grain & is a source of Fiber. It is high in Calcium & Protein that is essential for your child’s growing body.
Kellogg’s Moons & Stars is enriched with 10 essential vitamins & minerals like Iron, Zinc, B Vitamins & Vitamin C for your active kids.
Kellogg’s Chocos Moons & Stars + 200ml cow’s milk provides 66% of the day’s RDA for Calcium and 31% of the day’s RDA for Protein
